public class QuestionEditor
extends JFrame
implements ChangeListener, ListSelectionListener, TableModelListener

A specialized editor for a Question. The layout is described in QuestionEditor.yml.

addBlank

private void addBlank()
Adds a new blank to the JList and to the backend. Increments the fibBlankIndex to point to the new blank, and increment the fibBlankCount. Updates the buttons as necessary.

removeBlank

private void removeBlank()
Removes a blank from the JList and the backend. Decrements the fibBlankIndex if necessary, at the end of the list, and decrement the fibBlankCount. Updates the buttons as necessary.

addCorrectAnswer

private void addCorrectAnswer()
Adds a new correct answer to the JTable and to the backend. Increments the fibBlankCAIndex to point to the new choice, and increment the fibBlankCACount. Updates the buttons as necessary.

removeCorrectAnswer

private void removeCorrectAnswer()
Removes a correct answer from the JTable and the backend. Decrements the fibBlankCAIndex if necessary, at the end of the list, and decrement the fibBlankCACount. Updates the buttons as necessary.

moveUpCorrectAnswer

private void moveUpCorrectAnswer()
Moves a correct answer up the JTable. Cannot move a correct answer up that is at the beginning of the list.

moveDownCorrectAnswer

private void moveDownCorrectAnswer()
Moves a correct answer down the JTable. Cannot move a correct answer down that is at the end of the list.

setChoice

private void setChoice()
Sets the correct answer of the choice and marks it with a (*). Removes the marking off of the old answer.

editChoice

private void editChoice()
Edits the current choice pointed to by the JList if the index is valid. Creates a new JOptionPane in order to achieve this.

editChoice

Changes the message of the currently selected choice.

addChoice

private void addChoice()
Adds a new Choice to the JList and to the backend. Increments the mcChoiceIndex to point to the new choice, and increment the mcChoiceCount. Updates the buttons as necessary.

removeChoice

private void removeChoice()
Removes a Choice from the JList and the backend. Decrements the mcChoiceIndex if necessary, at the end of the list, and decrement the mcChoiceCount. Updates the buttons as necessary.

moveUpChoice

private void moveUpChoice()
Moves a Choice up the JList. Cannot move a choice up that is at the beginning of the list.

moveDownChoice

private void moveDownChoice()
Moves a Choice down the JList. Cannot move a choice down that is at the end of the list.

updateTable

private void updateTable()
Changes the correct answers table so that it points to a new blank. Should be called after the blank index is changed.

validateData

private void validateData()
Validates data to make sure that data was entered correctly. The FIB question must have the # of blanks match the number of "___."s.
